e and Unity Event in London with Yousaf Islam, Jermaine Jackson and Imran\nKhan, 2008 World Peace for Life Concert in Los Angeles with Christina Applegate\nand Michael Beckwith, 2005 Reviving the Spirit of Islam in Toronto along with\nSami Yousaf, and 2011 ISNA in Chicago, along with renowned singers of peace. For\nhis services to the community on the platform of he was presented two\ncongressional awards in 2006 and 2007 in the USA. He is also the goodwill\nambassador for ANF (Anti Narcotics Force) of Pakistan. His powerful âHum Bolain\nMohabbat Ki Zubanâ was used as the ââFace of Pakistanââ on CNN World by the\nPakistan government. . Currently he is working on his first English spiritual\nalbum in Canada and promoting his world peace song âOnly Love,â co-written with\nhit songwriter Chris Eaton (number 1s for Cliff Richard and Janet Jackson).\n\nâI believe that the Muslim world and the West both have a lot to share and\noffer, so itâs vital to develop common grounds and evolve together for a better\nand peaceful future for our children for generations to come.â â Najam Sheraz\n","linknr":151,"url":"Najam_Sheraz","recorded":1364146928,"links":["/w/index.php?title=Najam_Sheraz&action=edit","/w/index.php?title=Najam_Sheraz&action=edit","//en.wikipedia.org/apple-touch-icon.png","//bits.wikimedia.org/favicon/wikipedia.ico","/w/opensearch_desc.php","//en.wikipedia.org/w/api.php?action=rsd","//creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/","/w/index.php?title=Special:RecentChanges&feed=atom","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=ext.gadget.DRN-wizard%2CReferenceTooltips%2Ccharinsert%2Cteahouse%7Cext.wikihiero%7Cmediawiki.legacy.commonPrint%2Cshared%7Cmw.PopUpMediaTransform%7Cskins.vector&only=styles&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=site&only=styles&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=startup&only=scripts&